Package bt.Model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Bittorrent
    Bittorrent is the main class for the client.
    Peer
    Creates a connection with a peer to download a file.
    PeerListener
    The main listener thread for each peer this client is connected to.
    PeerSpooler
    It will be in charge of spooling, choking and unchoking peers every N amount of time.
    Request
    This class serves as an immutable storage object for an incoming request.
    Server
    This class will initiate a new thread as the server side of the Bittorrent client.
    Timer<T extends Timed>
    This class will function as a generic timer for any object which implements timed interface.
    TrackerRefresher
    This class will contact the Tracker periodically for refreshing event status and peers list.
